ğŸ“– Description

This project is an Arduino-based robot that combines line following and obstacle avoidance behaviors.
The robot follows a black line using IR sensors and automatically avoids obstacles using an ultrasonic sensor.
The entire circuit and logic were simulated using Wokwi.

